title: raised back of hand: dark skin tone

adjectives: Increased, particularly above a normal level.
verbs: Raise the level or amount of something
nouns: A return made with the back of the hand facing the direction of the stroke
The backhand is a tennis shot in which one swings the racquet around one's body with the back of the hand preceding the palm.
A stroke made across the chest from the off-hand side to the racquet hand side; a stroke during which the back of the hand faces the shot.

description: This version of the  Raised Back of Hand emoji has the  Dark Skin Tone applied, which is displayed as a Black Skin Tone on supported pla
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the dark skin tone raised back of hand emoji is presented with a subtle, yet definitive gesture, its surface subtly reflecting light with Apple's signature glossy 3D shading. The soft rounded edges of the knuckles and the palm side, rendered with realistic lighting, give it a tactile and grounded appearance. This emoji often signifies a firm 'stop,' a high five, or a strong affirmation, conveying a sense of authority and solidarity through Apple's refined design.
